1
00:00:01,001 --> 00:00:03,002
<b>[Althea]</b><i><b> I miss you so much, Erica.</b></i>

2
00:00:03,086 --> 00:00:06,631
<b>[sniffles] </b><i><b>If only</b></i>
<i><b>none of this happened…</b></i>

3
00:00:08,341 --> 00:00:10,635
<i><b>Are you and Erica better now?</b></i>

4
00:00:10,719 --> 00:00:12,846
<i><b>I don't know if my visit helped.</b></i>

5
00:00:12,929 --> 00:00:15,849
<i><b>I don't know how we can ever be okay.</b></i>

6
00:00:15,932 --> 00:00:19,644
<i><b>Sometimes, I still think</b></i>
<i><b>about the things I didn't get to do.</b></i>

7
00:00:19,728 --> 00:00:24,733
<i><b>But if you strip away my insecurities,</b></i>
<i><b>this is the life I want.</b></i>

8
00:00:24,816 --> 00:00:27,235
<i><b>Erica, something happened.</b></i>

9
00:00:27,318 --> 00:00:28,319
<i><b>What happened?!</b></i>

10
00:00:28,403 --> 00:00:30,405
<i><b>When I got home, Christina was alone.</b></i>

11
00:00:30,488 --> 00:00:33,033
<i><b>-Althea was gone.</b></i>
<b>-[Annette] </b><i><b>We need to find her.</b></i>

12
00:00:33,116 --> 00:00:36,202
<i><b>Help! There's a body</b></i>
<i><b>over there! I think they're dead!</b></i>

13
00:00:36,828 --> 00:00:37,746
<b>[Alice]</b><i><b> Erica…</b></i>

14
00:00:37,829 --> 00:00:43,835
<b>[ominous music playing]</b>

15
00:00:45,462 --> 00:00:51,926
<b>[theme music playing]</b>

16
00:02:01,162 --> 00:02:02,997
<b>[sinister music playing]</b>

17
00:02:03,081 --> 00:02:04,833
<b>A… Althea?</b>

18
00:02:04,916 --> 00:02:08,461
<b>[breathing shakily]</b>

19
00:02:16,219 --> 00:02:17,762
<b>[Alice] Althea?</b>

20
00:02:19,264 --> 00:02:20,473
<b>Althea.</b>

21
00:02:20,557 --> 00:02:23,643
<b>-[breathing shakily]</b>
<b>-[music becomes dramatic]</b>

22
00:02:23,726 --> 00:02:24,894
<b>Erica!</b>

23
00:02:25,895 --> 00:02:26,813
<b>Erica!</b>

24
00:02:26,896 --> 00:02:31,776
<b>[dramatic music continues]</b>

25
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:33,778
<b>[young Erica] </b><i><b>Luisa.</b></i>
<i><b>Hang in there, okay?</b></i>

26
00:02:33,862 --> 00:02:35,446
<i><b>Please stay with us.</b></i>

27
00:02:36,614 --> 00:02:40,535
<i><b>Louisa!</b></i><b> [wailing]</b>

28
00:02:40,618 --> 00:02:42,412
<i><b>-This can't be!</b></i>
<b>-[Alice] Erica, she's still alive!</b>

29
00:02:43,496 --> 00:02:44,497
<b>Althea!</b>

30
00:02:45,957 --> 00:02:46,833
<b>Erica!</b>

31
00:02:47,792 --> 00:02:48,668
<b>Erica!</b>

32
00:02:49,377 --> 00:02:50,420
<b>Erica!</b>

33
00:02:50,503 --> 00:02:52,589
<b>[siren blaring]</b>

34
00:02:52,672 --> 00:02:53,590
<b>Althea.</b>

35
00:02:53,673 --> 00:02:55,466
<b>[Alice] We have to</b>
<b>get her to the hospital.</b>

36
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:56,634
<b>Althea.</b>

37
00:02:56,718 --> 00:02:58,469
<b>Help! Help!</b>

38
00:02:58,553 --> 00:03:00,263
<b>Please help us!</b>

39
00:03:00,346 --> 00:03:01,806
<b>-[siren blaring]</b>
<b>-[Alice breathing shakily]</b>

40
00:03:01,890 --> 00:03:03,474
<b>-[Alice] Help!</b>
<b>-Hurry up!</b>

41
00:03:03,558 --> 00:03:05,685
<b>-Call an ambulance!</b>
<b>-Quick!</b>

42
00:03:05,768 --> 00:03:07,645
<b>-What happened?</b>
<b>-My goodness!</b>

43
00:03:07,729 --> 00:03:09,105
<b>[Alice] Get help!</b>

44
00:03:09,188 --> 00:03:10,523
<b>Help!</b>

45
00:03:10,607 --> 00:03:13,651
<b>[Annette] Althea, my dear, hang in there!</b>
<b>Just keep fighting!</b>

46
00:03:13,735 --> 00:03:15,737
<b>[sobbing]</b>

47
00:03:15,820 --> 00:03:17,989
<b>Please stay strong!</b>

48
00:03:18,072 --> 00:03:19,782
<b>-Ma'am, I'm sorry.</b>
<b>-My dear!</b>

49
00:03:19,866 --> 00:03:21,492
<b>You're not allowed to go in there.</b>

50
00:03:21,576 --> 00:03:22,827
<b>[Annette] Why?</b>

51
00:03:22,911 --> 00:03:24,120
<b>[sobbing]</b>

52
00:03:24,203 --> 00:03:25,246
<b>My dear!</b>

53
00:03:25,330 --> 00:03:29,876
<b>[dramatic music continues]</b>

54
00:03:29,959 --> 00:03:34,088
<b>My dear! [wailing]</b>

55
00:03:37,133 --> 00:03:38,426
<b>[Althea] </b><i><b>But as for me,</b></i>

56
00:03:38,509 --> 00:03:41,179
<i><b>I'm celebrating</b></i>
<i><b>your presence in this world.</b></i>

57
00:03:41,262 --> 00:03:42,931
<i><b>I'm thankful to you, Erica.</b></i>

58
00:03:45,016 --> 00:03:47,352
<i><b>Even though I'm no</b></i>
<i><b>longer part of your life.</b></i>

59
00:03:49,187 --> 00:03:50,939
<i><b>I miss you so much, Erica.</b></i>

60
00:03:51,022 --> 00:03:52,482
<i><b>Not just what we used to be like,</b></i>

61
00:03:52,565 --> 00:03:56,319
<i><b>but also what we could've been like now</b></i>

62
00:03:57,237 --> 00:03:59,822
<i><b>if those things didn't happen.</b></i>

63
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:02,450
<b>[Annette] My dear!</b>

64
00:04:03,743 --> 00:04:05,203
<b>My dear…</b>

65
00:04:05,286 --> 00:04:11,042
<b>-[Annette wailing]</b>
<b>-[Erica breathing shakily]</b>

66
00:04:11,125 --> 00:04:16,756
<b>[Erica sobbing]</b>

67
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:17,882
<b>Erica.</b>

68
00:04:17,966 --> 00:04:19,092
<b>Erica!</b>

69
00:04:22,428 --> 00:04:24,847
<b>There, there, Erica.</b>

70
00:04:26,015 --> 00:04:27,350
<b>Erica.</b>

71
00:04:30,019 --> 00:04:32,522
<b>She tried reaching</b>
<b>out to me so many times.</b>

72
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:36,276
<b>She begged me to accept her.</b>

73
00:04:36,359 --> 00:04:38,903
<b>-[Erica sobbing]</b>
<b>-[poignant music playing]</b>

74
00:04:38,987 --> 00:04:42,240
<b>She even cried last night because…</b>

75
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:45,660
<b>she said she missed me.</b>

76
00:04:47,912 --> 00:04:49,163
<b>Doesn't she know…</b>

77
00:04:50,581 --> 00:04:53,543
<b>that everyone who gets</b>
<b>close to me ends up like this?</b>

78
00:04:54,919 --> 00:04:57,046
<b>I'm no help to anyone.</b>

79
00:04:57,130 --> 00:04:59,048
<b>I'm no savior.</b>

80
00:04:59,924 --> 00:05:02,552
<b>I couldn't even save my own sister!</b>

81
00:05:03,303 --> 00:05:05,221
<b>-Erica, that's not true.</b>
<b>-No.</b>

82
00:05:06,097 --> 00:05:07,348
<b>No, Erica.</b>

83
00:05:08,433 --> 00:05:10,184
<b>Didn't her mother warn her?</b>

84
00:05:10,268 --> 00:05:12,145
<b>She shouldn't have gotten close to me.</b>

85
00:05:13,187 --> 00:05:16,691
<b>This wouldn't have</b>
<b>happened if she stayed away from me.</b>

86
00:05:17,525 --> 00:05:19,068
<b>Shh…</b>

87
00:05:24,574 --> 00:05:32,081
<b>-[Erica sobbing]</b>
<b>-[tender music playing]</b>

88
00:05:32,165 --> 00:05:33,249
<b>[Erica sniffles]</b>

89
00:05:38,421 --> 00:05:39,464
<b>[Erica sniffles]</b>

90
00:05:44,177 --> 00:05:46,763
<b>[Erica sniffles]</b>

91
00:05:50,183 --> 00:05:52,226
<b>[sobbing]</b>

92
00:05:52,310 --> 00:06:00,359
<b>[tender music continues]</b>

93
00:06:01,736 --> 00:06:04,864
<b>[sobbing]</b>

94
00:06:08,785 --> 00:06:09,911
<b>My dear…</b>

95
00:06:17,627 --> 00:06:24,300
<b>-[tender music continues]</b>
<b>-[both sobbing]</b>

96
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:31,140
<b>[reporter] </b><i><b>Breaking news!</b></i>

97
00:06:31,224 --> 00:06:34,477
<i><b>After the discovery</b></i>
<i><b>of Esther Castro's body</b></i>

98
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:37,939
<i><b>and the murder of</b></i>
<i><b>Anton Montenegro here in Amurao,</b></i>

99
00:06:38,022 --> 00:06:41,234
<i><b>20-year-old Althea Encio,</b></i>

100
00:06:41,317 --> 00:06:44,237
<i><b>sister of famous lawyer Erica Melendez,</b></i>

101
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:46,948
<i><b>is now fighting for</b></i>
<i><b>her life in the hospital</b></i>

102
00:06:47,031 --> 00:06:49,492
<i><b>after being slashed in the neck.</b></i>

103
00:06:49,575 --> 00:06:51,953
<i><b>Everyone's suspecting</b></i>
<i><b>only one person as the culprit</b></i>

104
00:06:52,036 --> 00:06:54,747
<i><b>behind the series</b></i>
<i><b>of attacks in our town…</b></i>

105
00:06:54,831 --> 00:06:57,750
<i><b>the escaped prisoner Edong Santiago,</b></i>

106
00:06:57,834 --> 00:07:01,295
<i><b>who seems determined to</b></i>
<i><b>cause bloodshed in Amurao.</b></i>

107
00:07:01,379 --> 00:07:02,088
<b>[Edong grunts]</b>

108
00:07:02,171 --> 00:07:03,714
<b>[reporter]</b>
<i><b>Everyone should remain vigilant</b></i>

109
00:07:03,798 --> 00:07:05,883
<i><b>until he is caught.</b></i>

110
00:07:05,967 --> 00:07:07,093
<i><b>Amurao Police,</b></i>

111
00:07:07,176 --> 00:07:09,512
<i><b>-please move quickly!</b></i>
<b>-Was I the one who did this?</b>

112
00:07:09,595 --> 00:07:10,888
<b>[high-pitched ringing]</b>

113
00:07:10,972 --> 00:07:13,057
<b>No… It wasn't me.</b>

114
00:07:13,141 --> 00:07:15,685
<b>I wasn't the one who did this. No!</b>

115
00:07:16,769 --> 00:07:19,856
<b>I had nothing to do with it! No!</b>

116
00:07:21,566 --> 00:07:26,237
<b>[foreboding music playing]</b>

117
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:28,656
<b>[Edward] </b><i><b>Althea is on her way, too.</b></i>

118
00:07:28,739 --> 00:07:30,741
<i><b>Her father will be dropping her off.</b></i>

119
00:07:30,825 --> 00:07:33,786
<i><b>I just couldn't turn</b></i>
<i><b>down the church's request.</b></i>

120
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:37,123
<i><b>But I'll be right back after a few hours.</b></i>

121
00:07:37,206 --> 00:07:43,796
<b>[foreboding music continues]</b>

122
00:07:45,423 --> 00:07:46,757
<b>[car lock beeps]</b>

123
00:07:54,348 --> 00:07:56,434
<i><b>-Good evening, Sir Edward.</b></i>
<b>-[Edward] </b><i><b>Good evening.</b></i>

124
00:08:01,189 --> 00:08:02,398
<b>[car lock beeps]</b>

125
00:08:05,943 --> 00:08:07,570
<b>[car engine starts]</b>

126
00:08:07,653 --> 00:08:14,243
<b>-[foreboding music continues]</b>
<b>-[shovel thudding]</b>

127
00:08:34,972 --> 00:08:36,098
<b>[Edward grunts]</b>

128
00:08:44,232 --> 00:08:45,858
<b>[light footsteps]</b>

129
00:08:51,822 --> 00:08:53,074
<i><b>Is that you?</b></i>

130
00:08:53,157 --> 00:08:56,202
<b>-[music fades]</b>
<b>-[cicadas chirping]</b>

131
00:08:57,203 --> 00:08:58,913
<i><b>Did you think I wouldn't notice?</b></i>

132
00:09:01,624 --> 00:09:03,626
<i><b>I saw you that day.</b></i>

133
00:09:03,709 --> 00:09:10,258
<b>[uneasy music playing]</b>

134
00:09:28,818 --> 00:09:35,908
<b>[Edong laughing maniacally]</b>

135
00:09:40,288 --> 00:09:42,707
<b>[Edong] </b><i><b>How will Alice feel…</b></i>

136
00:09:43,624 --> 00:09:45,876
<i><b>when she finds out that you're a monster?</b></i>

137
00:09:46,669 --> 00:09:49,922
<b>[Edong laughing maniacally]</b>

138
00:09:50,006 --> 00:09:52,550
<b>[Edong] </b><i><b>Whose bones are those, huh?</b></i>

139
00:09:53,467 --> 00:09:55,678
<i><b>What did you do to that person?</b></i>

140
00:09:56,846 --> 00:09:59,098
<i><b>Poor Alice.</b></i>

141
00:09:59,932 --> 00:10:01,934
<i><b>She keeps running away from me,</b></i>

142
00:10:03,561 --> 00:10:05,938
<i><b>not knowing</b></i>

143
00:10:06,022 --> 00:10:09,650
<i><b>that the demon has</b></i>
<i><b>been clinging to her all this time.</b></i>

144
00:10:10,318 --> 00:10:12,194
<b>[footsteps approaching]</b>

145
00:10:13,237 --> 00:10:15,114
<b>[dramatic music sting]</b>

146
00:10:15,197 --> 00:10:19,994
<b>[uneasy music continues]</b>

147
00:10:22,455 --> 00:10:24,373
<i><b>I thought you were sent…</b></i>

148
00:10:25,041 --> 00:10:27,418
<i><b>to protect Alice</b></i>

149
00:10:28,711 --> 00:10:31,964
<i><b>and prevent me from hurting her friends.</b></i>

150
00:10:33,591 --> 00:10:35,885
<i><b>But you're no protector.</b></i>

151
00:10:36,969 --> 00:10:38,888
<i><b>You want to kill, too.</b></i>

152
00:10:44,977 --> 00:10:51,859
<b>-[laughing maniacally]</b>
<b>-[sinister music playing]</b>

153
00:10:59,742 --> 00:11:00,993
<i><b>Just like you?</b></i>

154
00:11:01,077 --> 00:11:06,832
<b>[uneasy music continues]</b>

155
00:11:06,916 --> 00:11:09,627
<i><b>I'm not like you.</b></i>

156
00:11:09,710 --> 00:11:11,253
<b>[Edward] </b><i><b>Oh, really?</b></i>

157
00:11:12,254 --> 00:11:14,173
<i><b>I know your story, Edong.</b></i>

158
00:11:15,758 --> 00:11:20,888
<i><b>My father was just like yours.</b></i>

159
00:11:22,348 --> 00:11:25,643
<i><b>But my father didn't only beat me up.</b></i>

160
00:11:25,726 --> 00:11:28,771
<i><b>He did something extra to me.</b></i>

161
00:11:29,814 --> 00:11:34,110
<i><b>Something that I'm sure</b></i>
<i><b>your father didn't do to you.</b></i>

162
00:11:34,193 --> 00:11:37,696
<b>[uneasy music continues]</b>

163
00:11:37,780 --> 00:11:39,490
<i><b>My father…</b></i>

164
00:11:40,616 --> 00:11:42,827
<i><b>loved children in a special way.</b></i>

165
00:11:43,828 --> 00:11:47,289
<i><b>And the one he loved the most…</b></i>

166
00:11:50,126 --> 00:11:51,168
<i><b>was me.</b></i>

167
00:11:53,921 --> 00:11:55,506
<i><b>So, whatever I am now…</b></i>

168
00:11:57,508 --> 00:11:59,677
<i><b>I got it all from my father.</b></i>

169
00:12:00,803 --> 00:12:03,264
<i><b>You're a… menace.</b></i>

170
00:12:03,347 --> 00:12:09,311
<b>[uneasy music continues]</b>

171
00:12:11,814 --> 00:12:12,815
<i><b>Why…</b></i>

172
00:12:15,151 --> 00:12:17,361
<i><b>don't we work together, Edong?</b></i>

173
00:12:19,321 --> 00:12:21,532
<i><b>I'll help you kill</b></i>

174
00:12:21,615 --> 00:12:25,077
<i><b>-anyone who--</b></i>
<i><b>-Anyone?</b></i>

175
00:12:27,329 --> 00:12:30,249
<i><b>I don't just kill anyone.</b></i>

176
00:12:31,876 --> 00:12:33,586
<i><b>I have a mission!</b></i>

177
00:12:36,046 --> 00:12:38,340
<i><b>I was given</b></i>
<i><b>a second chance at life for that.</b></i>

178
00:12:44,221 --> 00:12:45,097
<i><b>Okay.</b></i>

179
00:12:48,309 --> 00:12:50,519
<i><b>I'll help you</b></i>
<i><b>accomplish your mission, Edong.</b></i>

180
00:12:52,229 --> 00:12:54,773
<i><b>You know I can easily do that.</b></i>

181
00:12:57,526 --> 00:12:59,695
<i><b>I'm close to that group of friends.</b></i>

182
00:13:01,614 --> 00:13:03,949
<i><b>They have complete trust in me.</b></i>

183
00:13:04,033 --> 00:13:06,118
<b>[Edward laughing maniacally]</b>

184
00:13:06,202 --> 00:13:09,747
<i><b>Everything will be</b></i>
<i><b>easier if we work together, right?</b></i>

185
00:13:11,665 --> 00:13:13,083
<i><b>But in exchange,</b></i>

186
00:13:15,586 --> 00:13:17,463
<i><b>you have to keep quiet about everything…</b></i>

187
00:13:18,422 --> 00:13:20,841
<i><b>everything you've seen here.</b></i>

188
00:13:23,594 --> 00:13:29,892
<b>[laughing maniacally]</b>

189
00:13:34,313 --> 00:13:38,192
<i><b>Just imagine how much Alice would cry…</b></i>

190
00:13:39,026 --> 00:13:41,529
<i><b>when she finds out</b></i>
<i><b>what kind of person you are.</b></i>

191
00:13:42,821 --> 00:13:48,160
<i><b>It's so satisfying</b></i>
<i><b>to watch her fall apart.</b></i>

192
00:13:48,244 --> 00:13:50,162
<b>[tense music sting]</b>

193
00:13:50,246 --> 00:13:52,289
<i><b>So, you should…</b></i>

194
00:13:52,873 --> 00:13:54,625
<i><b>die.</b></i>

195
00:13:54,708 --> 00:13:55,834
<b>[grunts]</b>

196
00:13:55,918 --> 00:14:01,549
<b>[laughing maniacally]</b>

197
00:14:01,632 --> 00:14:05,553
<b>-[grunting]</b>
<b>-[blow lands]</b>

198
00:14:06,220 --> 00:14:07,680
<b>-[thwacks]</b>
<b>-[groans]</b>

199
00:14:08,556 --> 00:14:09,848
<b>-[grunting]</b>
<b>-[kick lands]</b>

200
00:14:09,932 --> 00:14:11,517
<b>-[body thuds]</b>
<b>-[groans]</b>

201
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:13,352
<b>-[thwacks]</b>
<b>-[pants]</b>

202
00:14:13,435 --> 00:14:14,937
<b>[grunting]</b>

203
00:14:15,020 --> 00:14:20,442
<b>[tense music playing]</b>

204
00:14:20,526 --> 00:14:22,152
<b>[grunting]</b>

205
00:14:26,365 --> 00:14:30,035
<b>[laughing maniacally]</b>

206
00:14:31,370 --> 00:14:32,746
<b>-[kick lands]</b>
<b>-[body thuds]</b>

207
00:14:35,791 --> 00:14:37,626
<b>[yells]</b>

208
00:14:37,710 --> 00:14:40,045
<b>[grunts, groans]</b>

209
00:14:40,129 --> 00:14:43,299
<b>[grunting]</b>

210
00:14:46,719 --> 00:14:48,721
<b>[tense music continues]</b>

211
00:14:48,804 --> 00:14:50,848
<i><b>I just received this.</b></i>

212
00:14:51,807 --> 00:14:53,809
<i><b>I haven't even used it yet.</b></i>

213
00:14:54,768 --> 00:14:56,812
<i><b>Maybe this was given to me…</b></i>

214
00:14:58,772 --> 00:15:00,941
<i><b>to use on you.</b></i>

215
00:15:13,704 --> 00:15:20,961
<b>[tense music continues]</b>

216
00:15:22,254 --> 00:15:24,048
<i><b>Edong, just think about this.</b></i>

217
00:15:25,090 --> 00:15:30,054
<i><b>You and I are on the same side.</b></i>

218
00:15:31,263 --> 00:15:33,641
<i><b>As I've said…</b></i>

219
00:15:34,683 --> 00:15:37,519
<i><b>I'm not like you.</b></i>

220
00:15:39,271 --> 00:15:40,564
<i><b>I have a mission.</b></i>

221
00:15:40,648 --> 00:15:42,942
<b>[ominous music playing]</b>

222
00:15:43,025 --> 00:15:45,903
<i><b>I was given a second chance…</b></i>

223
00:15:46,862 --> 00:15:50,658
<i><b>to make them pay for their sins.</b></i>

224
00:15:54,078 --> 00:15:58,666
<i><b>A menace like you will never be chosen!</b></i>

225
00:15:58,749 --> 00:16:00,084
<i><b>You're right.</b></i>

226
00:16:00,167 --> 00:16:02,836
<b>[breathing heavily]</b>

227
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:04,588
<i><b>We're not the same.</b></i>

228
00:16:06,131 --> 00:16:08,175
<i><b>You take after your father.</b></i>

229
00:16:10,010 --> 00:16:12,888
<i><b>Your father is back.</b></i>

230
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:16,517
<i><b>He has returned to Amurao.</b></i>

231
00:16:20,187 --> 00:16:22,106
<i><b>Liar.</b></i>

232
00:16:22,189 --> 00:16:24,108
<i><b>Check it.</b></i>

233
00:16:24,191 --> 00:16:26,610
<i><b>Go to the police station.</b></i>

234
00:16:26,694 --> 00:16:28,988
<i><b>-He's locked up there now.</b></i>
<b>-[Edong gasps]</b>

235
00:16:29,071 --> 00:16:35,995
<b>-[ominous music continues]</b>
<b>-[breathing sharply]</b>

236
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:38,414
<b>[breathes deeply]</b>

237
00:16:39,081 --> 00:16:40,332
<b>[both grunt]</b>

238
00:16:40,416 --> 00:16:42,084
<b>[exhales deeply, grunts]</b>

239
00:16:42,167 --> 00:16:45,921
<b>-[panting]</b>
<b>-[hurried footsteps]</b>

240
00:16:46,005 --> 00:16:52,344
<b>[ominous music continues]</b>

241
00:16:52,428 --> 00:16:59,435
<b>[indistinct chatter]</b>

242
00:17:04,690 --> 00:17:06,775
<b>[policeman] </b><i><b>Good evening, ma'am.</b></i>

243
00:17:06,859 --> 00:17:07,985
<b>-[radio beeps]</b>
<i><b>-Hello.</b></i>

244
00:17:08,068 --> 00:17:08,777
<i><b>Unit 12…</b></i>

245
00:17:08,861 --> 00:17:10,029
<i><b>-Guerrero!</b></i>
<i><b>-Requesting immediate backup.</b></i>

246
00:17:10,112 --> 00:17:11,530
<i><b>There was a shootout</b></i>
<i><b>in Barangay San Felipe.</b></i>

247
00:17:11,613 --> 00:17:13,866
<i><b>Officers down! Repeat, officers down!</b></i>

248
00:17:13,949 --> 00:17:15,909
<b>[radio beeping]</b>

249
00:17:16,618 --> 00:17:18,495
<i><b>San Felipe? It's not that far, right?</b></i>

250
00:17:18,579 --> 00:17:20,205
<i><b>But we still don't have backup here.</b></i>

251
00:17:20,289 --> 00:17:22,291
<i><b>They said backup's five minutes away.</b></i>

252
00:17:22,374 --> 00:17:25,878
<i><b>I think we should leave now.</b></i>
<i><b>We need to be in San Felipe.</b></i>

253
00:17:25,961 --> 00:17:31,383
<b>[ominous music intensifies]</b>

254
00:17:32,176 --> 00:17:38,766
<b>-[police siren blaring]</b>
<b>-[stirring music playing]</b>

255
00:17:42,936 --> 00:17:44,354
<b>-[policeman] </b><i><b>Hey, Noy.</b></i>
<i><b>-Sir…</b></i>

256
00:17:44,438 --> 00:17:45,773
<i><b>Where are my combat shoes?</b></i>

257
00:17:45,856 --> 00:17:47,649
<i><b>Last time I checked,</b></i>
<i><b>it's already being stitched.</b></i>

258
00:17:47,733 --> 00:17:49,234
<i><b>I'll have it polished.</b></i>

259
00:17:49,318 --> 00:17:51,653
<i><b>That's why I like you. What's that?</b></i>

260
00:17:51,737 --> 00:17:53,864
<i><b>Ah, I bought this for my playmates.</b></i>

261
00:17:53,947 --> 00:17:55,574
<i><b>The knocked-down prisoners!</b></i>

262
00:17:55,657 --> 00:17:57,367
<i><b>Silly kid. Come in.</b></i>

263
00:17:57,451 --> 00:18:03,957
<b>-[paper bag rustling]</b>
<b>-[stirring music continues]</b>

264
00:18:07,878 --> 00:18:10,047
<i><b>Hey, it's time to eat!</b></i>

265
00:18:10,130 --> 00:18:11,256
<b>[prisoner giggles]</b>

266
00:18:11,340 --> 00:18:12,925
<i><b>-Give me some.</b></i>
<i><b>-Let's eat.</b></i>

267
00:18:13,008 --> 00:18:18,514
<b>[stirring music continues]</b>

268
00:18:18,597 --> 00:18:23,685
<b>[stirring music crescendos]</b>

269
00:18:23,769 --> 00:18:25,145
<i><b>Where's my food?</b></i>

270
00:18:25,813 --> 00:18:29,108
<i><b>Huh? What are you doing, huh?!</b></i>

271
00:18:29,775 --> 00:18:30,859
<i><b>What's that for?</b></i>

272
00:18:31,318 --> 00:18:33,278
<i><b>He asked me to record you.</b></i>

273
00:18:35,114 --> 00:18:36,281
<i><b>Who?</b></i>

274
00:18:36,865 --> 00:18:37,991
<i><b>Edmundo.</b></i>

275
00:18:38,075 --> 00:18:45,999
<b>[ominous music playing]</b>

276
00:18:53,132 --> 00:18:55,217
<b>[Crisanto] </b><i><b>What are you doing, huh?!</b></i>

277
00:18:57,886 --> 00:18:59,138
<b>[breathes sharply]</b>

278
00:19:00,472 --> 00:19:01,932
<i><b>What's that for?</b></i>

279
00:19:02,891 --> 00:19:05,102
<b>[Noy] </b><i><b>He asked me to record you.</b></i>

280
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:07,688
<i><b>Who?</b></i>

281
00:19:09,273 --> 00:19:11,024
<b>[Noy] </b><i><b>Edmundo.</b></i>

282
00:19:12,317 --> 00:19:13,277
<i><b>He's here?</b></i>

283
00:19:14,027 --> 00:19:15,237
<b>[Noy] </b><i><b>You're in trouble.</b></i>

284
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:18,574
<i><b>-He looked mad at you.</b></i>
<b>-[breathes deeply]</b>

285
00:19:18,657 --> 00:19:19,700
<b>[Crisanto] </b><i><b>Ah…</b></i>

286
00:19:20,659 --> 00:19:22,369
<i><b>He's mad at me?</b></i>

287
00:19:24,329 --> 00:19:25,998
<i><b>He probably thinks…</b></i>

288
00:19:27,124 --> 00:19:29,459
<i><b>I'm unaware of what he's up to.</b></i>

289
00:19:31,837 --> 00:19:34,173
<b>-[breathes sharply]</b>
<b>-[Crisanto] </b><i><b>I knew it.</b></i>

290
00:19:36,258 --> 00:19:38,468
<i><b>You'd end up just like me.</b></i>

291
00:19:40,470 --> 00:19:42,472
<i><b>You're really my son.</b></i>

292
00:19:42,556 --> 00:19:43,974
<b>[snickers]</b>

293
00:19:45,225 --> 00:19:47,394
<i><b>We're exactly the same.</b></i>

294
00:19:48,979 --> 00:19:51,607
<b>-[Edong huffs]</b>
<b>-[Crisanto chuckles lightly]</b>

295
00:19:53,150 --> 00:19:55,027
<b>[breathes sharply] No.</b>

296
00:19:58,322 --> 00:20:00,240
<i><b>You're also a murderer.</b></i>

297
00:20:01,533 --> 00:20:04,036
<i><b>You also like hurting women, right?</b></i>

298
00:20:04,119 --> 00:20:11,084
<b>[foreboding music playing]</b>

299
00:20:13,712 --> 00:20:15,714
<b>I only did that…</b>

300
00:20:17,174 --> 00:20:19,343
<b>…to accomplish my mission.</b>

301
00:20:21,261 --> 00:20:22,554
<i><b>Now…</b></i>

302
00:20:23,472 --> 00:20:25,766
<i><b>you understand…</b></i>

303
00:20:25,849 --> 00:20:28,352
<i><b>why I did that to your mother.</b></i>

304
00:20:28,977 --> 00:20:30,020
<b>No.</b>

305
00:20:30,103 --> 00:20:32,898
<b>[music becomes somber]</b>

306
00:20:32,981 --> 00:20:34,149
<b>No.</b>

307
00:20:36,151 --> 00:20:38,612
<b>[breathes shakily] No.</b>

308
00:20:38,695 --> 00:20:41,073
<b>[inhales shakily] No.</b>

309
00:20:43,408 --> 00:20:46,620
<b>No!</b>

310
00:20:47,079 --> 00:20:49,498
<b>[grunts, screams]</b>

311
00:20:49,581 --> 00:20:53,752
<b>-[groaning loudly, screaming]</b>
<b>-[blows landing]</b>

312
00:20:53,835 --> 00:20:59,132
<b>-[groaning, sobbing loudly]</b>
<b>-[somber music continues]</b>

313
00:20:59,216 --> 00:21:02,135
<b>I- I didn't do that! I swear!</b>

314
00:21:02,219 --> 00:21:04,054
<b>[sobs]</b>

315
00:21:04,137 --> 00:21:05,639
<b>I didn't do that!</b>

316
00:21:05,722 --> 00:21:07,849
<b>[Crisanto] </b><i><b>You like hurting women, right?</b></i>

317
00:21:07,933 --> 00:21:10,102
<b>[sobs] No!</b>

318
00:21:10,185 --> 00:21:12,896
<b>I said I didn't do that!</b>

319
00:21:12,980 --> 00:21:16,692
<b>[Crisanto] </b><i><b>Now, you understand…</b></i>
<i><b>why I did that to your mother.</b></i>

320
00:21:18,694 --> 00:21:21,863
<b>[sobs] Why me?!</b>

321
00:21:21,947 --> 00:21:29,371
<b>-[sobbing shakily]</b>
<b>-[somber music continues]</b>

322
00:21:30,247 --> 00:21:32,499
<b>[sobbing loudly]</b>

323
00:21:33,166 --> 00:21:38,213
<b>[wails] No!</b>

324
00:21:42,634 --> 00:21:45,262
<b>[music fades]</b>

325
00:21:50,309 --> 00:21:51,685
<b>Do you think it's Edong?</b>

326
00:21:51,768 --> 00:21:57,024
<b>[unsettling music playing]</b>

327
00:21:57,107 --> 00:21:59,443
<b>They said it's very</b>
<b>similar to Louisa's case.</b>

328
00:22:01,236 --> 00:22:04,406
<b>So, if Edong really did</b>
<b>this… [breathes sharply]</b>

329
00:22:04,489 --> 00:22:07,159
<b>does this mean he's</b>
<b>the one who killed Louisa?</b>

330
00:22:08,785 --> 00:22:13,415
<b>Or did he purposely mimic her murder</b>
<b>to send us a message?</b>

331
00:22:13,915 --> 00:22:16,793
<b>[clears throat]</b>
<b>But the timing's just right, isn't it?</b>

332
00:22:16,877 --> 00:22:19,212
<b>It happened right</b>
<b>after your press conference.</b>

333
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:21,715
<b>This might be the answer to what you said.</b>

334
00:22:25,552 --> 00:22:27,054
<b>Am I right, Beth?</b>

335
00:22:27,721 --> 00:22:31,349
<b>[pensive music playing]</b>

336
00:22:31,433 --> 00:22:33,101
<b>Actually…</b>

337
00:22:33,185 --> 00:22:35,020
<b>we're not sure, Uncle.</b>

338
00:22:36,354 --> 00:22:38,857
<b>Marco and Lucas are</b>
<b>now at the crime scene.</b>

339
00:22:39,566 --> 00:22:42,194
<b>Maybe they'll find</b>
<b>something that clears everything up.</b>

340
00:22:42,694 --> 00:22:46,239
<b>[pensive music continues]</b>

341
00:22:46,323 --> 00:22:48,492
<b>[sighs] I hope Althea</b>
<b>gets through all this.</b>

342
00:22:49,117 --> 00:22:50,994
<b>She's like a daughter to us.</b>

343
00:22:53,288 --> 00:22:55,624
<b>[Edward sighs, sniffles]</b>

344
00:22:55,707 --> 00:22:58,168
<b>We've finished</b>
<b>performing the patient's surgery.</b>

345
00:22:59,419 --> 00:23:02,297
<b>There's a knife cut</b>
<b>on the side of her neck.</b>

346
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:03,840
<b>But the good news is that…</b>

347
00:23:03,924 --> 00:23:06,176
<b>no major artery has been damaged.</b>

348
00:23:07,135 --> 00:23:10,847
<b>The patient lost consciousness</b>
<b>due to the amount of blood she had lost.</b>

349
00:23:10,931 --> 00:23:12,432
<b>Hypovolemic shock.</b>

350
00:23:13,016 --> 00:23:15,018
<b>But, in my initial exam,</b>

351
00:23:15,102 --> 00:23:16,937
<b>I found no brain damage.</b>

352
00:23:17,020 --> 00:23:20,232
<b>[somber music playing]</b>

353
00:23:20,315 --> 00:23:21,274
<b>However…</b>

354
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:24,945
<b>the patient is in</b>
<b>a medically induced coma.</b>

355
00:23:25,028 --> 00:23:26,696
<b>She needs to rest</b>

356
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:28,323
<b>so the swelling subsides</b>

357
00:23:28,406 --> 00:23:30,826
<b>and her oxygen levels stabilize.</b>

358
00:23:30,909 --> 00:23:32,536
<b>It'll probably take a few days.</b>

359
00:23:33,203 --> 00:23:36,248
<b>As of now, whether she can survive</b>
<b>rests on her own strength.</b>

360
00:23:37,040 --> 00:23:38,083
<b>Oh.</b>

361
00:23:38,166 --> 00:23:45,006
<b>-[sniffling]</b>
<b>-[somber music continues]</b>

362
00:23:45,090 --> 00:23:47,217
<b>[Edong] </b><i><b>You couldn't</b></i>
<i><b>do anything, Attorney.</b></i>

363
00:23:47,300 --> 00:23:48,426
<b>[snickering]</b>

364
00:23:48,510 --> 00:23:51,930
<i><b>All you can do now</b></i>
<i><b>is watch them cry in rage</b></i>

365
00:23:52,013 --> 00:23:53,723
<i><b>as they lose everything.</b></i>

366
00:23:53,807 --> 00:23:56,434
<i><b>You're useless. You're worthless.</b></i>

367
00:23:56,518 --> 00:23:58,937
<i><b>You're not a savior.</b></i>

368
00:23:59,020 --> 00:24:00,480
<i><b>Attorney…</b></i>

369
00:24:02,023 --> 00:24:04,109
<i><b>You're a fake hero.</b></i>

370
00:24:04,192 --> 00:24:10,907
<b>-[high-pitched ringing]</b>
<b>-[heart thumping]</b>

371
00:24:12,284 --> 00:24:14,744
<b>Erica, where are you going?</b>

372
00:24:15,245 --> 00:24:16,496
<b>Erica!</b>

373
00:24:16,580 --> 00:24:21,334
<b>[high-pitched ringing crescendos]</b>

374
00:24:22,252 --> 00:24:24,171
<b>You're dealing with two cases, aren't you?</b>

375
00:24:24,254 --> 00:24:26,673
<b>[tense music playing]</b>

376
00:24:26,756 --> 00:24:28,884
<b>Robbery with homicide in Cavite.</b>

377
00:24:28,967 --> 00:24:30,468
<b>And parricide in Amurao.</b>

378
00:24:31,094 --> 00:24:33,305
<b>You'll rot in prison.</b>

379
00:24:35,473 --> 00:24:37,475
<b>[inhales deeply]</b>
<b>But that can still be changed.</b>

380
00:24:39,186 --> 00:24:40,896
<b>I knew it.</b>

381
00:24:41,730 --> 00:24:43,565
<b>You need something from me.</b>

382
00:24:44,399 --> 00:24:46,151
<b>What is it, Attorney?</b>

383
00:24:47,652 --> 00:24:50,030
<b>I need your cooperation in catching Edong.</b>

384
00:24:50,113 --> 00:24:57,662
<b>[tense music continues]</b>

385
00:25:08,131 --> 00:25:11,718
<i><b>I really have a bad feeling</b></i>
<i><b>about that entrapment for Edong.</b></i>

386
00:25:11,801 --> 00:25:14,846
<i><b>Even if we catch Edong,</b></i>
<i><b>if he's not the one who killed Louisa,</b></i>

387
00:25:14,930 --> 00:25:17,515
<i><b>then that means</b></i>
<i><b>the killer is still out there.</b></i>

388
00:25:17,599 --> 00:25:20,310
<i><b>Edong will end up killing more people</b></i>
<i><b>if we don't do this!</b></i>

389
00:25:20,393 --> 00:25:22,020
<i><b>We need him to catch Edong.</b></i>

390
00:25:22,103 --> 00:25:23,897
<i><b>Erica, he killed my mother!</b></i>

391
00:25:23,980 --> 00:25:26,316
<b>[Edong] </b><i><b>Why didn't you tell me?</b></i>

392
00:25:26,399 --> 00:25:30,070
<i><b>Why did you take him to the police?</b></i>
<i><b>You should have brought him to me.</b></i>

393
00:25:30,153 --> 00:25:32,155
<i><b>You're right, Edong.</b></i>
<i><b>We should be the ones to take revenge.</b></i>

394
00:25:32,239 --> 00:25:33,531
<i><b>Help me.</b></i>

395
00:25:33,615 --> 00:25:36,952
<b>[tense music swells]</b>
